			.navbar-inner
				.container
					a.btn.btn-navbar(data-toggle='collapse', data-target='.nav-collapse')
						span.icon-bar
						span.icon-bar
						span.icon-bar
					a.brand(href='./')= site_name_lower
					.nav-collapse
						ul.nav.pull-right
							li
								a(href='/manager-login') Manager Login
							li
								a(href='/login') Employee Login
		.container
			.row
				.span6
					h1= site_name
					p Schedule.me can help any business that employs part-time, shift work employees. We provide a seamless way to deliver schedules to employees, and make it easier for your employees to trade or get rid of shifts when necessary.
					p If you would like to discuss how Schedule.me can work with your business, please contact me at 
						a(href='mailto:nrmitchi@gmail.com') nrmitchi@gmail.com
			.row
				.span12
					h3 Features:
				.span4
					.well
						h4 Instant Publishing
						p Your employees will be notified as soon as schedules are published, and we able to access their schedules from any web-enabled device
				.span4
					.well
						h4 Easy Upload
						p You can easily upload your schedule in whatever format your scheduler uses. If your format is not currently supported, we will work quickly to get it working for you
				.span4
					.well
						h4 Easy Trading
						p Your employees can easily offer shifts to co-workers and pick up extra shifts when needed, with you having the final say on all changes.